{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-template-js","path":"/pajama shirt/","result":{"pageContext":{"id":"7cffeedf-d050-5f8c-b2a2-670ab7ad3e00","html":"<h1>pajama shirt</h1>\n<p><em>march 2026</em></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/817ac881aeeec67bd7f34b90261c6d0d/d3c45/hippari-closeup.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"close-up of blue linen fabric with a fancy leaf shaped stitch in yellow thread\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/817ac881aeeec67bd7f34b90261c6d0d/1c72d/hippari-closeup.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/817ac881aeeec67bd7f34b90261c6d0d/a80bd/hippari-closeup.jpg 148w,\n/static/817ac881aeeec67bd7f34b90261c6d0d/1c91a/hippari-closeup.jpg 295w,\n/static/817ac881aeeec67bd7f34b90261c6d0d/1c72d/hippari-closeup.jpg 590w,\n/static/817ac881aeeec67bd7f34b90261c6d0d/a8a14/hippari-closeup.jpg 885w,\n/static/817ac881aeeec67bd7f34b90261c6d0d/fbd2c/hippari-closeup.jpg 1180w,\n/static/817ac881aeeec67bd7f34b90261c6d0d/d3c45/hippari-closeup.jpg 3472w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>i made a set of pajamas over thanksgiving 2025 at my parents' but i improvised the shirt and it was kinda bad.</p>\n<p>so i bought a <a href=\"https://www.folkwear.com/products/japanese-field-clothing\">hippari pattern</a> because that looked like it would be an interesting shirt to use as pajamas.</p>\n<p>i got blue linen and also i had bought a sewing machine for my new apartment because why would i want to <em>not</em> have a tool lying around?</p>\n<p>i made a muslin that came out decent so i just did the real one as soon as the blue arrived. after i was done i figured the fancy leaf stitch would look good around the edges with yellow thread so i did that on a slower speed.</p>\n<p>todo: picture of it being worn if i am brave enough for that</p>"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}